  "lines": [
    "[section:Verse 1]",
    "From this [G]valley they say you are going",
    "We will [C]miss your bright eyes and sweet [G]smile",
    "For they say you are taking the sunshine",
    "That has [D7]brightened our path for a [G]while",
    "",
    "[section:Chorus]",
    "Come and [G]sit by my side if you love me",
    "Do not [C]hasten to bid me a[G]dieu",
    "But remember the Red River Valley",
    "And the [D7]cowboy who loved you so [G]true",
    "",
    "[section:Verse 2]",
    "Won't you [G]think of the valley you're leaving",
    "Oh how [C]lonely, how sad it will [G]be",
    "Oh think of the fond heart you're breaking",
    "And the [D7]grief you are causing to [G]me"
  ],
